Global Agriculture Controlled Release Fertilizers Granule Market Insights
Agriculture Controlled Release Fertilizers Granule Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 6.1 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Agriculture Controlled Release Fertilizers Granule Market Overview
The global market for Agriculture Controlled Release Fertilizers Granules was valued at approximately USD 5.9 billion in 2023, with expectations of growth at a CAGR of 6.1% from 2024 to 2030. These fertilizers are designed to release nutrients gradually, optimizing plant growth and reducing environmental impact. The industry has experienced robust demand due to the increasing need for sustainable agricultural practices, environmental protection, and crop yield enhancement. Growing investments in precision farming and the development of advanced granules are expected to drive further market expansion.

